      <guid>https://jackwu925.github.io/posts/life-records/2024/0807/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: left; line-height: 200%; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 15px;&#34;&gt;
At USTC after a rainstorm, I tried to take a time-lapse of a rainbow while having dinner, so I left my camera next to the window. Although there was no rainbow in the end, the finished video was quite a surprise!😄
